CodeDef upper Filter
CodeDef upper Alias uc

CodeDef uc Filter
CodeDef uc Description Upper case
CodeDef uc Routine <<EOR
sub {
	use locale;
	if ($Scratch->{mv_locale}) {
	    POSIX::setlocale(LC_CTYPE, $Scratch->{mv_locale});
	}
	return uc(shift);
}
EOR
